  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/e5b937e05ea3383fc8dd3a37f4e8194a.avif?t=1749017874\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras_big/e5b937e05ea3383fc8dd3a37f4e8194a.avif?t=1749017874 width=800 height=228 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game looks simple, but it's ruthless on the inside. Tricky mechanics are waiting to catch you, and one wrong move could send you straight back to the bottom! But don't worry, you can try as many times as you want, <strong>so get stronger (mentally) each time you fall!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The feeling of despairing over your mistakes, yet gradually improving, is incredibly addictive. If that's you, then <strong>you're definitely a special person!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/38abfcf106d5384e55f9ac1ba3019391.poster.avif?t=1749017874\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/38abfcf106d5384e55f9ac1ba3019391.webm?t=1749017874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/38abfcf106d5384e55f9ac1ba3019391.mp4?t=1749017874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And just when you think climbing is all there is, you’re in for an even more hellish... no, ultimate stage! Whether you’ll reach it depends on your skill! If you've made it this far, don’t run away now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge again and again, fall again and again, and in the end, laugh! \"Riseon\" – Are you ready to take on this challenge?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The ultra-tough jumping action is here!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/15747bd0431b4790d9fe12e68cdcb3f9.avif?t=1749017874\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras_big/15747bd0431b4790d9fe12e68cdcb3f9.avif?t=1749017874 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/f352f6e4a2445b269d9477dbd3f8b30b.avif?t=1749017874\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras_big/f352f6e4a2445b269d9477dbd3f8b30b.avif?t=1749017874 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■Guidelines for Submitting and Distributing Our Game Content</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SHINKURO VALLEY Corp. appreciates customers who wish to use game footage<br>from our titles to create engaging videos that enrich their lives,<br>and we support their entertainment activities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > (Our games can be posted and distributed without permission by any individual or corporation.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please refer to the official “Riseon” website for more information.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/e5b937e05ea3383fc8dd3a37f4e8194a.avif?t=1749017874\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras_big/e5b937e05ea3383fc8dd3a37f4e8194a.avif?t=1749017874 width=800 height=228 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game looks simple, but it's ruthless on the inside. Tricky mechanics are waiting to catch you, and one wrong move could send you straight back to the bottom! But don't worry, you can try as many times as you want, <strong>so get stronger (mentally) each time you fall!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The feeling of despairing over your mistakes, yet gradually improving, is incredibly addictive. If that's you, then <strong>you're definitely a special person!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/38abfcf106d5384e55f9ac1ba3019391.poster.avif?t=1749017874\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/38abfcf106d5384e55f9ac1ba3019391.webm?t=1749017874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/38abfcf106d5384e55f9ac1ba3019391.mp4?t=1749017874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And just when you think climbing is all there is, you’re in for an even more hellish... no, ultimate stage! Whether you’ll reach it depends on your skill! If you've made it this far, don’t run away now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge again and again, fall again and again, and in the end, laugh! \"Riseon\" – Are you ready to take on this challenge?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The ultra-tough jumping action is here!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/15747bd0431b4790d9fe12e68cdcb3f9.avif?t=1749017874\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras_big/15747bd0431b4790d9fe12e68cdcb3f9.avif?t=1749017874 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras/f352f6e4a2445b269d9477dbd3f8b30b.avif?t=1749017874\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542790/extras_big/f352f6e4a2445b269d9477dbd3f8b30b.avif?t=1749017874 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■Guidelines for Submitting and Distributing Our Game Content</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SHINKURO VALLEY Corp. appreciates customers who wish to use game footage<br>from our titles to create engaging videos that enrich their lives,<br>and we support their entertainment activities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > (Our games can be posted and distributed without permission by any individual or corporation.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please refer to the official “Riseon” website for more information.</p>",
